Ask HN: What do I do about LastPass and how do I switch?
text: After using LastPass for many years, I have more than a thousand passwords stored in it.  It's too many to make it practical to manually change them all.  Is there a way to get all of them into something else, like BitWarden, and then [semi]automatically change them all?
